## Session Workflow

<!-- How agents should work in this workspace. -->

1. **Start:** Read CLAUDE.md and key context files
2. **Understand:** Confirm understanding of the request
3. **Work:** Execute the task using available tools (files, database, web search, code)
4. **Deliver:** Provide results in the appropriate format
5. **Update:** If the work changes any context files, update them
